## Slide 3 — How It Works

> Simple. Secure. Instant.

```
You Type Naturally              ──►  AI Understands Your Intent
"Set up a database for orders"  ──►  Creates DynamoDB table instantly
"Start the backup server"       ──►  Starts EC2 instance in seconds
"Store our files in Mumbai"     ──►  Creates S3 bucket in ap-south-1
```

**3-step process:**

| Step | What Happens |
|---|---|
| 1️⃣ **Connect** | Securely link your AWS account — one time setup |
| 2️⃣ **Type** | Describe what you need in plain English |
| 3️⃣ **Done** | Your cloud resource is created, managed, or updated |

---

## Slide 4 — What You Can Manage

> One platform. All your cloud services.

| Service | What You Can Do |
|---|---|
| 🗃️ **Storage (S3)** | Create, list, upload, delete files and folders |
| ⚡ **Compute Functions (Lambda)** | Deploy & run business logic — no servers needed |
| 🖥️ **Servers (EC2)** | Start, stop, and monitor your virtual machines |
| 🔐 **Access Control (IAM)** | Manage team permissions and security roles |
| 🗄️ **Database (DynamoDB)** | Create and query your databases instantly |
| 📨 **Messaging (SQS/SNS)** | Send notifications and connect your applications |
| 📊 **Monitoring (CloudWatch)** | View alarms and performance metrics at a glance |

> **All 8 AWS services. One chat interface. Zero complexity.**

