## Slide 6 — Security & Reliability

> Enterprise-grade security. Always.

- 🔐 **Credentials never stored** — kept in memory only, cleared on logout
- 🛡️ **Rate limiting** — protects against abuse and accidental overuse
-  **Verified connections** — every login validated against AWS's own security system (STS)
- 🗺️ **Region-aware** — all operations run in your chosen AWS region
- 📋 **Full audit trail** — every action logged with timestamp and response time

